Uses of Package
com.javatoavalla.model

  • Packages that use com.javatoavalla.model 
    Package Description
    com.javatoavalla.avallascenario
    This package provides interfaces and classes related to scenarios, including the mapping of scenario objects to scenario files and writing functionality.
    com.javatoavalla.avallascenario.impl
    This package contains implementations of the interfaces defined in the avallaScenario package.
    com.javatoavalla.filewriter
    This package contains the interface and implementation for writing ScenarioFile objects to a file.
    com.javatoavalla.filewriter.impl
    This package contains the implementation of the classes inside the fileWriter package.
    com.javatoavalla.javascenario
    This package contains classes and interfaces that define and manage the scenarios in a Java environment.
    com.javatoavalla.javascenario.impl
    This package contains the implementation classes for managing scenarios in the Java environment.
    com.javatoavalla.javascenario.listener
    This package contains listener-based classes for parsing and processing scenarios.
  • Classes in com.javatoavalla.model used by com.javatoavalla.avallascenario
